-- POLL-ECB to allot 120 billion euros at 7-day refi op
-- By Jonathan Cable
-- Mon Dec 29, 2014 07:21AM EST
-- None



LONDON, Dec 29 (Reuters) - The European Central Bank will allot 120 billion euros at its last weekly seven-day refinancing operation of the year, according to a Reuters poll published on Monday.

That is around the same amount as the 119.16 billion euros  ($145 billion) maturing from last week. [ID:nZYN0LCC24]  ----------------------------------------------------------------   ALLOTMENT ONE-WEEK   ---------------------------------------------------------------  MEDIAN120.0   MEAN  119.7   MODE  125.0   HIGHEST   140.0   LOWEST 97.0COUNT21